{"id":104,"title":"测试用例设计流程","slug":"测试用例设计流程-1766595076","excerpt":"","content":"## 一、总体流程\n\n\n\n\n\n## 二、核心设计方法\n\n## 1. 等价类划分（Equivalence Partitioning）\n\n\n\n\n\n## 2. 边界值分析（Boundary Value Analysis）\n\n\n\n\n\n## 3. 决策表测试（Decision Table Testing）\n\n\n\n\n\n## 4. 状态转换测试（State Transition Testing）\n\n\n\n\n\n## 5. 场景测试 \u0026 探索式测试\n\n\n\n\n\n## 6. Pairwise / N‑wise 组合测试\n\n\n\n\n\n## 7. 白盒覆盖（Code‑based Coverage）\n\n\n\n\n\n### 方法选型速查表\n\n\n\n\u003e 最佳实践： 通常组合 2‑3 种方法以平衡覆盖与成本。如 “需求→决策表→等价类/边界→自动生成 Pairwise 数据→白盒补漏”，再用场景测试收尾。\n\n\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:51:16.336364+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:51:16.336364+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f45d23c-2eec-809d-a3b4-f66e88471307","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-18T09:41:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":104,"blog_post_id":104,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.627131+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.627131+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:51:16.336364+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:51:16.336364+08:00"}